BARRIERS TO GROWTH FACING THE MEDIUM-SIZED COMPANY
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Ranked by order of significance
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
 1. Overall growth of market demand
 1. Increasing competiton
 2. Management skills
 3. Availability and cost of overdraft finance
 5. Marketing and sales skills
 6. Availability and cost of finance for expansion
 7. Skilled labour
 8. Difficulties in implementing new technology
 9. Acquisition of new technology
10. Access to overseas markets
11. Availability of appropriate premises of site
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
