FT  22 FEB 93 / Observer: Over-monitored
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Meanwhile, some good news on the EC job-creation front. The Commission has
decided to monitor the EC Monitor programme which monitors EC research
expenditures. In other words the Community's research boffins are being
asked to monitor how well Monitor is monitoring them. It's a true
Community-wide initiative. The questionnaire comes from Brussels, replies go
to Spain, and the Danish ministry of industry is providing the chairman of
the review panel.
